uccess is never smooth. Popular recently released an ‘Ep’ titled “Who is Popular” and is currently working on few projects and collaborations that would be announced soon. Check Out The Latest Track By Popular titled “PARA“, produced by Dr Syk. Proudly Powered by Dailytrendtv. Enjoy!!! Don’t Forget To Share with your friends and family… https://tooxclusive.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Popular-PaRa.mp3 DOWNLOAD MP3 Follow Popular on his social media handles.Instagram and Twitter: @popularisloud The post Popular – “Para” (Prod. by Dr Syk) appeared first on tooXclusive.